The question is, what is it different from the employee book?

55:29.000 --> 55:31.000
Once again,

55:31.000 --> 55:33.000
the employee book is something created,

55:33.000 --> 55:35.000
structured,

55:35.000 --> 55:37.000
having a single structure

55:37.000 --> 55:39.000
and high-quality content.

55:39.000 --> 55:41.000
As for the set of a beginner,

55:41.000 --> 55:43.000
this set can include something else besides the book.

55:43.000 --> 55:45.000
Maybe you don't have a book,

55:45.000 --> 55:47.000
and there is a number of separate documents

55:47.000 --> 55:49.000
that you collect

55:49.000 --> 55:51.000
for the arrival of a new employee.

55:51.000 --> 55:53.000
The set of a beginner can include

