By the way, a very important point

56:03.000 --> 56:05.000
that I have not yet mentioned,

56:05.000 --> 56:07.000
and I will definitely mention it,

56:07.000 --> 56:09.000
is that when developing such tools,

56:09.000 --> 56:11.000
whether it is a welcome training,

56:11.000 --> 56:13.000
a training for professionals,

56:13.000 --> 56:15.000
PR and marketing departments,

