56:29.000 --> 56:31.000
and their tools,

56:31.000 --> 56:33.000
their brochures

56:33.000 --> 56:35.000
are aimed at them.

56:35.000 --> 56:37.000
Our clients,

56:37.000 --> 56:39.000
the clients of the staff service,

56:39.000 --> 56:41.000
are the employees.

56:41.000 --> 56:43.000
And very often,

56:43.000 --> 56:45.000
the tools of the marketing department,

56:45.000 --> 56:47.000
a beautiful brochure,

56:47.000 --> 56:49.000
are good as an additional material,

56:49.000 --> 56:51.000
but not as a single one.

56:51.000 --> 56:53.000
Because, once again,

56:53.000 --> 56:55.000
we have a different target audience.

56:55.000 --> 56:57.000
Not external clients,

56:57.000 --> 56:59.000
but employees.

56:59.000 --> 57:01.000
The next one is the first day of a new employee.

