We talked about the fact

57:03.000 --> 57:05.000
that you need to prepare for this day.

57:05.000 --> 57:07.000
There should be a ready workplace.

57:07.000 --> 57:09.000
It should be a place for a predecessor.

57:09.000 --> 57:11.000
Some piles of papers,

57:11.000 --> 57:13.000
broken pencils,

57:13.000 --> 57:15.000
and so on.

57:15.000 --> 57:17.000
It clearly shows

57:17.000 --> 57:19.000
that a person worked

57:19.000 --> 57:21.000
very actively.

57:21.000 --> 57:23.000
This is not what you need.

57:23.000 --> 57:25.000
If your company has such things

57:25.000 --> 57:27.000
as badges that can be prepared in advance,

57:27.000 --> 57:29.000
it will be great if it is done.

57:29.000 --> 57:31.000
Very often people ask

57:31.000 --> 57:33.000
what badges, we have not yet taken a picture.

