a sign of welcome

58:01.000 --> 58:03.000
from colleagues is prepared.

58:03.000 --> 58:05.000
It can be a small chocolate,

58:05.000 --> 58:07.000
a bag of nuts,

58:07.000 --> 58:09.000
or something else.

58:09.000 --> 58:11.000
It is very good

58:11.000 --> 58:13.000
to have such a sign of welcome.

58:13.000 --> 58:15.000
It will influence

58:15.000 --> 58:17.000
a good impression

58:17.000 --> 58:19.000
of a new employee

58:19.000 --> 58:21.000
from all of us.

58:21.000 --> 58:23.000
Once again,

58:23.000 --> 58:25.000
we do not forget

58:25.000 --> 58:27.000
that the first few days

58:27.000 --> 58:29.000
of a week

58:29.000 --> 58:31.000
and a month

58:31.000 --> 58:33.000
of a company employee

58:33.000 --> 58:35.000
are not only

58:35.000 --> 58:37.000
when we look at him,

58:37.000 --> 58:39.000
but also when he looks at us.

58:39.000 --> 58:41.000
That is why you have achieved success

58:41.000 --> 58:43.000
if on the first day

58:43.000 --> 58:45.000
a company employee

58:45.000 --> 58:47.000
is proud and has an inner positivity.

58:47.000 --> 58:49.000
The next point

58:49.000 --> 58:51.000
is to introduce a new employee.

58:51.000 --> 58:53.000
Colleagues, there are two aspects.

58:53.000 --> 58:55.000
First,

58:55.000 --> 58:57.000
we have to introduce

58:57.000 --> 58:59.000
an employee to the workers.

58:59.000 --> 59:01.000
At the same time,

59:01.000 --> 59:03.000
we have to introduce

59:03.000 --> 59:05.000
a new employee to his team

59:05.000 --> 59:07.000
and his future colleagues.

59:09.000 --> 59:11.000
It is clear that

59:11.000 --> 59:13.000
it is chaotic in companies.

59:13.000 --> 59:15.000
If you have introduced a new employee,

59:15.000 --> 59:17.000
it is like you have introduced him.

59:17.000 --> 59:19.000
If you have not introduced him,

59:19.000 --> 59:21.000
you can say that

59:21.000 --> 59:23.000
a brand manager is sitting here,

59:23.000 --> 59:25.000
an accountant is sitting there,

59:25.000 --> 59:27.000
and so on.

59:27.000 --> 59:29.000
But there were no such people.

59:29.000 --> 59:31.000
So,

59:31.000 --> 59:33.000
he should be prepared

59:33.000 --> 59:35.000
at the moment.

59:35.000 --> 59:37.000
First,

59:37.000 --> 59:39.000
if we are talking about introducing an employee,

59:39.000 --> 59:41.000
make sure to separate

59:41.000 --> 59:43.000
a regular employee from a new manager.

59:43.000 --> 59:45.000
If it is a regular employee,

59:45.000 --> 59:47.000
tell him something

59:47.000 --> 59:49.000
and introduce him to his closest circle.

59:49.000 --> 59:51.000
If it is a manager,

59:51.000 --> 59:53.000
the field of his future interaction

59:53.000 --> 59:55.000
will be larger.

59:55.000 --> 59:57.000
And the manager

59:57.000 --> 59:59.000
should be given more information

59:59.000 --> 01:00:01.000
because his subordinates

01:00:01.000 --> 01:00:03.000
and other employees

01:00:03.000 --> 01:00:05.000
are interested in it.

01:00:07.000 --> 01:00:09.000
If it is a top manager,

01:00:09.000 --> 01:00:11.000
it should not be

01:00:11.000 --> 01:00:13.000
given to the side.

01:00:13.000 --> 01:00:15.000
I recommend

01:00:15.000 --> 01:00:17.000
preparing so-called meeting plans

01:00:17.000 --> 01:00:19.000
which include

01:00:19.000 --> 01:00:21.000
specific information

01:00:21.000 --> 01:00:23.000
about the scheme,

01:00:23.000 --> 01:00:25.000
who, when and how.

01:00:25.000 --> 01:00:27.000
If it is a big company,

01:00:27.000 --> 01:00:29.000
it is possible to organize a video conference.

01:00:29.000 --> 01:00:31.000
Or it is possible

01:00:31.000 --> 01:00:33.000
to post an interview

01:00:33.000 --> 01:00:35.000
with a new manager

01:00:35.000 --> 01:00:37.000
in the website

01:00:37.000 --> 01:00:39.000
where he will answer questions

01:00:39.000 --> 01:00:41.000
and tell about his experience,

01:00:41.000 --> 01:00:43.000
biography and personal characteristics.

01:00:43.000 --> 01:00:45.000
It is necessary

01:00:45.000 --> 01:00:47.000
to introduce a manager.

01:00:47.000 --> 01:00:49.000
People are waiting for it.

01:00:49.000 --> 01:00:51.000
Very often, when a new manager comes,

01:00:51.000 --> 01:00:53.000
he will introduce a new method.

01:00:53.000 --> 01:00:55.000
It is important to remember

01:00:55.000 --> 01:00:57.000
that this feeling of fear

01:00:57.000 --> 01:00:59.000
should be replaced

01:00:59.000 --> 01:01:01.000
by a feeling of trust

01:01:01.000 --> 01:01:03.000
to facilitate

01:01:03.000 --> 01:01:05.000
the introduction of a manager

01:01:05.000 --> 01:01:07.000
to our team.

01:01:07.000 --> 01:01:09.000
Sometimes people ask

01:01:09.000 --> 01:01:11.000
how it is possible

01:01:11.000 --> 01:01:13.000
to introduce a manager

01:01:13.000 --> 01:01:15.000
to a big company

01:01:15.000 --> 01:01:17.000
and tell him

01:01:17.000 --> 01:01:19.000
to adapt to the new manager.

01:01:19.000 --> 01:01:21.000
It is clear that all this happens

01:01:21.000 --> 01:01:23.000
during a dialogue.

01:01:23.000 --> 01:01:25.000
You, as a manager,

01:01:25.000 --> 01:01:27.000
can offer tools.

01:01:27.000 --> 01:01:29.000
There is an Internet site,

01:01:29.000 --> 01:01:31.000
an e-mail,

01:01:31.000 --> 01:01:33.000
an opportunity to post an interview

01:01:33.000 --> 01:01:35.000
or a note about a position

01:01:35.000 --> 01:01:37.000
in corporate press.

01:01:37.000 --> 01:01:39.000
We have some options in companies.

01:01:39.000 --> 01:01:41.000
Do not forget to work on them.

01:01:41.000 --> 01:01:43.000
It is very important.

01:01:43.000 --> 01:01:45.000
At the same time,

01:01:45.000 --> 01:01:47.000
it is important

01:01:47.000 --> 01:01:49.000
not to overload people.

01:01:49.000 --> 01:01:51.000
If someone has a bad memory,

01:01:51.000 --> 01:01:53.000
a new employee

01:01:53.000 --> 01:01:55.000
will smile to everyone.

01:01:55.000 --> 01:01:57.000
It is important to identify

01:01:57.000 --> 01:01:59.000
the key people

01:01:59.000 --> 01:02:01.000
to work with.

01:02:01.000 --> 01:02:03.000
They can be

01:02:03.000 --> 01:02:05.000
key people

01:02:05.000 --> 01:02:07.000
from other departments.

01:02:07.000 --> 01:02:09.000
It is clear that it is necessary

01:02:09.000 --> 01:02:11.000
to introduce them to your department.

01:02:11.000 --> 01:02:13.000
It is good to introduce them

01:02:13.000 --> 01:02:15.000
to the higher management.

01:02:15.000 --> 01:02:17.000
The employee should know them.

01:02:17.000 --> 01:02:19.000
How else?

01:02:19.000 --> 01:02:21.000
They should know the managers

01:02:21.000 --> 01:02:23.000
of another level.

01:02:23.000 --> 01:02:25.000
The next tools

